{"tid":1732965,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「圍城打援」最佳破解方法 就只有「圍魏救趙」","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:10:40.000Z","uid":40072,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14f582b1dbb73a4f2208c8ee63fe7cc72aff6757","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"上策：圍魏救趙，攻所有大春袋同脅官員。<br />\n中策：裡應外合，集中一點突破。<br />\n下策：放棄理大。重新組織示威策略。<br />\n<br />\n最精銳示威者係理大就被當成係一舊誘餌（春袋）<br />\n<br />\n唔可以唔救，亦唔可以送死，所以要搵政府/班狗更大嘅（春袋）嚟破，睇邊個肯放手先。<br />\n<br />\n明顯普通佔路已經引唔起班警甴分兵，所以要搵更大嘅春袋：例如機場、禮賓府、甚至麻包袋所有官員，先有機會可以引到佢地分兵去救。<br />\n<br />\n而家真係行緊中策，但我覺得係難行，而且會俾班警甴打到援。所以係時候升級攞官員或警甴家屬嚟換。<br />\n<br />\n純兵法學術應用討論，不建議任何實際行動。<br />\n<br />\n利申：受咗傷嘅冷氣軍司"},{"pid":"bd6c76a2cddd7f644b6b1406e8898b9346dbc437","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"cb791c9436c9bf48b8aac5d2139a7f65755cbc94","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:57:06.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"fc4888abb521201649584ecc90aeba89d83f54b7","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"263e58921233ae560cb5d7f8f93348bed101bd45","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"68257c3ca45771e5b718311b678aa8ad42126983","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"27d81d4186eed619a39293fbf83afe36d7a42a16","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f9f88262826df4d019c89a018baba2bb8d1b673c","tid":1732965,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"332fe9a75339a700919078bd4eb67c26a69c3e3a","tid":1732965,"uid":54303,